{"tid":1245351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣太陽花運動點樣搞","createTime":"2019-06-20T09:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:47:49.000Z","uid":265924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab943ccb5ebc2f3fd994dfcb2c7fdf9ed4c7fea","tid":1245351,"uid":265924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"衝，定唔衝？衝左入去又點？<br />\n係咪先有個充分商議既機會，再民主決策，會好D？<br />\n&ldquo;咪搞啦，打仗吖嘛，邊有時間？&rdquo; 但打仗之前，係咪應該預留時間傾清楚D？<br />\n不妨重溫一下台灣太陽花運動。大量群衆一齊聚集搞野，但點搞，真係意見紛云，有時閙到頭崩額裂。他們當時模仿2011年佔領華爾街運動的《商討手勢》，方便群衆在室外集會時，可以實行最民主的決策方式。如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmBwBpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmBwBpg.jpg&h=fff7a5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有呢個報道可以參考：<br />\n太陽花運動舉行公民行動會議<br />\n<a href=\"http://nicecasio.pixnet.net/blog/post/361925594-%E6%89%8B%E8%AA%9E+3%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%A0%E9%A0%98%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88occu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnicecasio.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F361925594-%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AA%259E%2B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258D%25A0%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%2588occu&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=0f4e94a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://nicecasio.pixnet.net/blog/post/361925594-%E6%89%8B%E8%AA%9E+3%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%A0%E9%A0%98%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88occu</a>"},{"pid":"24d30b767310b160a33e131c8af560b1a2a21780","tid":1245351,"uid":50658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句, 人地假假地都係民選政府"},{"pid":"9daca95063f30b85411362de9b77b17ca748e76f","tid":1245351,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,